00px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">syahrir maulana</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>This article was co-produced with The Dividend Collectuh.</em></p> <p>Due to uncertainty surrounding interest rates and volatility in the 10-year treasury (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/US10Y\" title=\"United States 10-Year Bond Yield\">US10Y</a>), some REITs still present attractive entries for long-term investors.</p> <p>One REIT in particular, <b>American Assets Trust, Inc.</b></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742044-american-assets-trust-quality-small-cap-reit-no-one-is-talking-about-but-should", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 17:30:41"}, {"id": "4742041", "title": "Infineon: A Solid Play On AI, But Some Challenges Remain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Infineon Technologies AG Neubiberg\" data-id=\"1482891838\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482891838/image_1482891838.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/